| [[Esophageal stent]]
| [[File:SEMS endo.jpg|thumb|[[Esophagogastroduodenoscopy|Endoscopic]] image of a [[self-expanding metallic stent]] in an [[esophagus]], used to [[palliative care|palliatively]] treat [[esophageal cancer]] ]]
|-
| Biliary stent, providing [[bile drainage]]
| [[File:Biliary stent endo.jpg|thumb|Endoscopic image of a biliary stent seen protruding from the [[ampulla of Vater]] at the time of duodenoscopy]]
